// BaseLine
$colums:12
$gutter: (100% /$colums)* 0.05
$one: (100% / $colums)
$pc-1: 1000px
$large: 992px
$table: 600px
$mobile: 320px
// BaseLine
html
  color: #000000
body
  color: #000000
  font-size: 1em !important
  div
    box-sizing: border-box

// Grid
.container
  min-width: 320px
  max-width: 1200px
  margin: 0 auto
  .wrap
    width: 100%
    max-width: inherit
    display: flex
    flex-direction: row
    flex-wrap: wrap
    margin-bottom: .2rem
    padding-right: calc( #{$gutter} * 4 )
    padding-left:  calc( #{$gutter} * 4 )
    div
      padding: .3rem 0
      position: relative
      z-index: 1
      margin-left: $gutter
    @media (max-width: 318px)
      .col
        width: calc( (#{$one} * 6) - #{$gutter})
    @media ( min-width: $mobile) and (max-width: $table)
      .col
        &.s1
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 1) - #{$gutter})
        &.s2
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 2) - #{$gutter})
        &.s3
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 3) - #{$gutter})
        &.s4
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 4) - #{$gutter})
        &.s5
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 5) - #{$gutter})
        &.s6
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 6) - #{$gutter})
        &.s7
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 7) - #{$gutter})
        &.s8
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 8) - #{$gutter})
        &.s9
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 9) - #{$gutter})
        &.s10
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 10) - #{$gutter})
        &.s11
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 11) - #{$gutter})
        &.s12
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 12) - #{$gutter})
        &.lef-s1
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 1) + (#{$gutter} * 1))
        &.lef-s2
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 2) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-s3
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 3) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-s4
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 4) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-s5
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 5) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-s6
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 6) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-s7
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 7) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-s8
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 8) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-s9
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 9) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-s10
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 10) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-s11
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 11) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-s12
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 12) + #{$gutter})
    @media ( min-width: $table  )
      .col
        &.m1
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 1) - #{$gutter})
        &.m2
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 2) - #{$gutter})
        &.m3
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 3) - #{$gutter})
        &.m4
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 4) - #{$gutter})
        &.m5
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 5) - #{$gutter})
        &.m6
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 6) - #{$gutter})
        &.m7
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 7) - #{$gutter})
        &.m8
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 8) - #{$gutter})
        &.m9
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 9) - #{$gutter})
        &.m10
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 10) - #{$gutter})
        &.m11
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 11) - #{$gutter})
        &.m12
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 12) - #{$gutter})
        &.lef-m1
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 1) + (#{$gutter} * 1))
        &.lef-m2
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 2) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-m3
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 3) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-m4
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 4) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-m5
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 5) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-m6
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 6) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-m7
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 7) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-m8
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 8) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-m9
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 9) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-m10
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 10) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-m11
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 11) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-m12
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 12) + #{$gutter})
    @media ( min-width: $large  )
      .col
        &.l1
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 1) - #{$gutter})
        &.l2
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 2) - #{$gutter})
        &.l3
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 3) - #{$gutter})
        &.l4
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 4) - #{$gutter})
        &.l5
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 5) - #{$gutter})
        &.l6
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 6) - #{$gutter})
        &.l7
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 7) - #{$gutter})
        &.l8
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 8) - #{$gutter})
        &.l9
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 9) - #{$gutter})
        &.l10
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 10) - #{$gutter})
        &.l11
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 11) - #{$gutter})
        &.l12
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 12) - #{$gutter})
        &.lef-l1
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 1) + (#{$gutter} * 1))
        &.lef-l2
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 2) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-l3
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 3) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-l4
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 4) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-l5
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 5) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-l6
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 6) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-l7
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 7) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-l8
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 8) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-l9
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 9) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-l0
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 10) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-l11
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 11) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-l12
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 12) + #{$gutter})
    @media ( min-width: $pc-1  )
      .col
        &.xl1
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 1) - #{$gutter})
        &.xl2
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 2) - #{$gutter})
        &.xl3
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 3) - #{$gutter})
        &.xl4
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 4) - #{$gutter})
        &.xl5
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 5) - #{$gutter})
        &.xl6
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 6) - #{$gutter})
        &.xl7
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 7) - #{$gutter})
        &.xl8
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 8) - #{$gutter})
        &.xl9
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 9) - #{$gutter})
        &.xl10
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 10) - #{$gutter})
        &.xl11
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 11) - #{$gutter})
        &.xl12
          width: calc( (#{$one} * 12) - #{$gutter})
        &.lef-xl1
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 1) + (#{$gutter} * 1))
        &.lef-xl2
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 2) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-xl3
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 3) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-xl4
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 4) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-xl5
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 5) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-xl6
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 6) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-xl7
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 7) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-xl8
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 8) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-xl9
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 9) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-xl10
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 10) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-xl11
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 11) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-xl12
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 12) + #{$gutter})
// VerticalRythm

// EndVerticalRythm

//Animal-Rout
.anim
  animation: animationFrames linear 0.8s
  animation-iteration-count: 1
  transform-origin: 50% 50%
  -webkit-animation: animationFrames linear 0.8s
  -webkit-animation-iteration-count: 1
  -webkit-transform-origin: 50% 50%
  -moz-animation: animationFrames linear 0.8s
  -moz-animation-iteration-count: 1
  -moz-transform-origin: 50% 50%
  -o-animation: animationFrames linear 0.8s
  -o-animation-iteration-count: 1
  -o-transform-origin: 50% 50%
  -ms-animation: animationFrames linear 0.8s
  -ms-animation-iteration-count: 1
  -ms-transform-origin: 50% 50%

@keyframes animationFrames
  0%
    transform: translate(0px, 0px)

  15%
    transform: translate(1px, -10px)

  30%
    transform: translate(1px, 0px)

  45%
    transform: translate(1px, -10px)

  60%
    transform: translate(1px, 0px)

  75%
    transform: translate(1px, -5px)

  100%
    transform: translate(1px, 0px)

@-moz-keyframes animationFrames
  0%
    -moz-transform: translate(0px, 0px)

  15%
    -moz-transform: translate(1px, -10px)

  30%
    -moz-transform: translate(1px, 0px)

  45%
    -moz-transform: translate(1px, -10px)

  60%
    -moz-transform: translate(1px, 0px)

  75%
    -moz-transform: translate(1px, -5px)

  100%
    -moz-transform: translate(1px, 0px)

@-webkit-keyframes animationFrames
  0%
    -webkit-transform: translate(0px, 0px)

  15%
    -webkit-transform: translate(1px, -10px)

  30%
    -webkit-transform: translate(1px, 0px)

  45%
    -webkit-transform: translate(1px, -10px)

  60%
    -webkit-transform: translate(1px, 0px)

  75%
    -webkit-transform: translate(1px, -5px)

  100%
    -webkit-transform: translate(1px, 0px)

@-o-keyframes animationFrames
  0%
    -o-transform: translate(0px, 0px)

  15%
    -o-transform: translate(1px, -10px)

  30%
    -o-transform: translate(1px, 0px)

  45%
    -o-transform: translate(1px, -10px)

  60%
    -o-transform: translate(1px, 0px)

  75%
    -o-transform: translate(1px, -5px)

  100%
    -o-transform: translate(1px, 0px)

@-ms-keyframes animationFrames
  0%
    -ms-transform: translate(0px, 0px)

  15%
    -ms-transform: translate(1px, -10px)

  30%
    -ms-transform: translate(1px, 0px)

  45%
    -ms-transform: translate(1px, -10px)

  60%
    -ms-transform: translate(1px, 0px)

  75%
    -ms-transform: translate(1px, -5px)

  100%
    -ms-transform: translate(1px, 0px)
//Animal-Rout
